Setup
=====

SSL
---

Make a CA to sign service certs.
Make a CA to sign user auth certs.
Make and sign service certs.
Mount certs in a secret.

Apache
^^^^^^


User Auth Certs
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
run pulp-gen-ca-certificate
path is /etc/pki/pulp/ca.*
delete originals in base Dockerfile

